song_name: It Is Well With My Soul

version_description: This version adds the walk up chords (G, Gsus4, G2), corrects some of the lyrics, adds pick up lyrics and adjusts chord placement.
This is the closest I could get to the original with simple chords. The Bm7 is really a D with a B bass note.
